Package fileIOPackage

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ImagesIO
    This Class contains static methods to manipulate the images files (add and delete) that are browsed by the user
    MP3IO
    This class handles the MP3 files that are browsed by the user in the AddWindow & EditWindow particularly when the user wants to edit old / add new item to the subject
    SubjectIO
    This class retrieves the subjects' objects in specific directories with every run of the program and saves those objects when the program shuts off
